data.description: Welcome to your private sanctuary! This stunning 5-bedroom, 3.5-bathroom home seamlessly combines modern updates with the beauty of nature, providing the perfect blend of comfort and tranquility. The newly renovated kitchen is a culinary haven, featuring sleek countertops, modern appliances, and ample storage. It is sure to inspire your inner chef and make cooking a delightful experience. The spacious living areas are perfect for entertaining or simply relaxing with your loved ones. The open floor plan allows for plenty of natural light to fill the space, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere. Step outside into your tranquil backyard retreat and immerse yourself in nature. With mature trees and a backdrop of woods, your private backyard offers an ideal space for unwinding and enjoying the peace and serenity of the outdoors. It is also a great place to host gatherings and entertain guests. In addition to all these wonderful features, the basement of the home includes a "safe room" for added security and peace of mind. Overall, this home is a true sanctuary where you can find comfort, relaxation, and the perfect balance between modern living and natural beauty.
